{
  "chapter": "113",
  "title": "南越列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "赵佗立国",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">尉佗（赵佗）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">真定</span>人，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝时已经吞并了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，略取平定了<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">杨越</span>地区，设置了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桂林</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南海</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">象郡</span>三郡，把犯罪的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众流放到那里，与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人杂居共处了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十三岁（时长）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝时被任用为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南海龙川令</span>。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦二世\">二世（秦二世）</span>时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南海尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任嚣</span>生病将死，召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">龙川令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵佗</span>告诉他说：\"听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>等人起来作乱，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝无道，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>深受其苦，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘季</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴广</span>等人在<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">州郡</span>各自起兵聚众，如虎般争夺<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>一片混乱，不知何时才能安定，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪杰</span>们背叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝相继自立。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南海</span>偏僻遥远，我恐怕盗匪之兵会侵占土地到达这里，我想发兵断绝<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新道</span>，自我防备，等待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的变化，正好又病重。况且<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>背负山险，以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南海</span>为屏障，东西<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>，颇有些<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>人作辅佐，这也是一州之主，可以建立国家。郡中的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>没有值得交谈的人，所以召您前来告知。\" 随即任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>代行<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南海尉</span>的职事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任嚣\">嚣（任嚣）</span>死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>立即传下檄文告谕<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">横浦</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳山</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">湟谿关</span>说：\"盗兵将要到来，赶紧断绝道路集结兵力自守！\" 于是渐渐依法<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝所任命的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>，用自己的党羽担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">假守</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>灭以后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>立即<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>取吞并了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桂林</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">象郡</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">南越武王（赵佗）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>平定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>后，因为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>百姓劳苦，所以没有<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "佗称帝与归汉",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，派遣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>前去<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>王，与他<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>为信、互通使节，使<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">百越</span>和睦相处，不要成为南方边境的祸患，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>接壤。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕后\">高后（吕后）</span>时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>奏请禁止<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>边关互市<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁器</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>立我为王，互通使者财物，如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕后\">高后（吕后）</span>听信谗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>之言，把<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>区别对待，隔绝器物，这必定是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>王的主意，想倚仗<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>而兼并之为王，自己邀功。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>便自尊尊号为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">武帝（赵佗）</span>，发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>边邑，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>坏数县后离去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕后\">高后（吕后）</span>派遣<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">隆虑侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：隆虑侯灶\">灶（隆虑侯灶）</span>前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>讨。恰逢暑湿季节，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>大多染上瘟疫，军队无法越岭。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">岁馀（时长）</span>之后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕后\">高后（吕后）</span>去世，于是罢兵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>因此以武力威慑边境，又用财物贿赂<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西瓯</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">骆</span>等部族，使他们役属于己，东西延伸<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀里</span>。于是乘坐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄屋</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">左纛</span>的帝王车驾，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">称制</span>下令，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>天子等同。 到了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">孝文帝元年</span>，刚开始镇抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，派使者告谕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">四夷</span>自己从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>国前来即位的用意，宣扬盛德。于是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>父母的坟冢在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">真定</span>，就设置守邑，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">岁时（时长）</span>奉行祭祀。召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>的堂兄弟，尊其官职厚加赏赐以示宠遇。下诏命<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>等推举可以出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>的人，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>举荐<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">好畤</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>，说他在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先帝</span>时熟悉出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>的事。于是召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陆贾\">贾（陆贾）</span>任命为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span>，前去出使。借此责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为帝，不曾派一个使者前来回报。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>，王非常害怕，写信谢罪，说：\"<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>大长老臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>，前些日子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕后\">高后（吕后）</span>隔阂<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>，我私下怀疑<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>王谗害我，又远远听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕后\">高后（吕后）</span>把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗族</span>全部<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，挖开烧毁先人坟冢，因此自暴自弃，侵犯<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>边境。况且南方卑湿，处于<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>之中，东边的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>仅有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千人</span>之众也号称为王，西边的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">瓯骆</span>裸国也称王。老<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>妄自窃取帝号，聊以自娱，哪里敢让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天王</span>听闻呢！\" 于是叩头谢罪，愿意长久作为藩<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，奉献贡赋。于是下令国中说：\"我听说两个雄主不能并立，两位贤者不能同世。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>，是贤明的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。从今以后，废去帝制的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄屋</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">左纛</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>回朝禀报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>非常高兴。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>时，南越称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，派人朝请。然而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>在国内仍然暗中沿用旧的帝号，只在出使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>时，才称王朝命如同<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">建元四年</span>去世。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "空\n\n## [4] 空\n\n## [5] 文王胡守职称臣",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>的孙子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>继任为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>王。此时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>边邑，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>派人上书说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">两越</span>都是藩<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，不得擅自兴兵相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>兴兵侵犯我，我不敢兴兵，唯请<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>下诏决定。\" 于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>赞许<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>有义，能守职约，为之兴师，派遣两位<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>前去讨伐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>。军队还未越过山岭，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>王的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">馀善</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>前来投降，于是罢兵。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "空",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄助</span>前去向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>王宣谕其意，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>叩头说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>竟为臣兴兵讨伐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">闽越</span>，我死也无法报答这份恩德！\" 派遣<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>入朝宿卫。对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄助\">助（庄助）</span>说：\"国家刚遭侵扰，使者先走吧。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>正日夜整装准备入朝拜见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄助\">助（庄助）</span>走后，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>劝谏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴兵<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：闽越王郢\">郢（闽越王郢）</span>，也是借此震慑<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>。况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>从前说过，事奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>只要不失礼就行，总之不可以听信好言而入朝拜见。入朝拜见就不得再回来，这是亡国之势。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>称病，终究没有入朝拜见。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十馀岁（时长）</span>之后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>确实病重，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>请求回国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">胡（赵胡）</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胡\">文王（赵胡）</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "婴齐兴与吕嘉乱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>继位，就把他先祖<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">武帝（赵佗）</span>的印玺藏起来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>入朝宿卫时，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">娶</span>了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樛氏</span>的女子，生下儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵兴\">兴（赵兴）</span>。等到即位，上书请求<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樛氏</span>之女为王后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵兴\">兴（赵兴）</span>为嗣。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝多次派使者讽谕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>还喜欢擅自<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>戮放纵自己，害怕入朝会被要求遵用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">汉法</span>，比照内地<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，坚持称病，终究不入朝拜见。派儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">次公</span>入朝宿卫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵婴齐\">明王（赵婴齐）</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "空",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵兴\">兴（赵兴）</span>继位，他的母亲为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>还未做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>姬妾时，曾与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸陵</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安国少季</span>私通。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>去世后，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安国少季</span>前去谕告南越王及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王太后</span>入朝，比照内地<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>；派能言善辩的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谏大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">终军</span>等宣读朝廷的言辞，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">勇士</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏臣</span>等辅助其缺失，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">路博德</span>统率军队屯驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桂阳</span>，接应使者。王年纪小，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>人，曾与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安国少季</span>私通，使者到后又与她私通。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">国人</span>大多知道这件事，许多人都不依附<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>害怕祸乱起来，也想倚仗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的威势，多次劝王及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>请求归附汉朝。于是通过使者上书，请求比照内地<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三岁一朝（时长）</span>，撤除边境关卡。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>答应了，赐给其<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">银印</span>，以及<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span>的印信，其余官员允许自行任命。废除他们原有的<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">黥劓刑</span>，采用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">汉法</span>，比照内地<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。使者都留在南越镇抚。王、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王太后</span>整饰行装置办重礼，准备入朝。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "空",
      "text": "他们的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>年纪已老，辅佐三代王，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗族</span>中做官成为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀人</span>，男子都娶王室女子为妻，女子都嫁给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王子</span>兄弟及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span>，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苍梧</span>的秦王有姻亲关系。他在国中地位很重，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人信任他，许多人做他的耳目，深得民心超过王。王上书请求内属，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>多次劝谏阻止王，王不听。吕嘉便生叛心，多次称病不见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝使者。使者都注意<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>，但形势未能<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀他。王、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王太后</span>也害怕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>等人先发难，就摆下酒宴，借助汉使的权威，谋划<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>等人。使者们都向东而坐，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>面朝南坐，王面朝北坐，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>都面朝西坐，侍坐陪饮。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>的弟弟为将，率兵守候在宫外。酒过数巡，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝，对国家有利，而相<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>为何苦言不便呢？\" 以此激怒使者。使者互相观望狐疑，竟没有敢动手的。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>见耳目之势不妙，就起身离开。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>大怒，想用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矛</span>刺<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>，王阻止<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>于是出去，分兵与其弟之兵一起回到家中，称病，不肯见王及使者。于是暗中与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>策划作乱。王本来就无意<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>知道，所以<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>没有发动。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>有淫乱之行，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">国人</span>不依附，想独自<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>等人，力量又不够。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "吕嘉反叛弑王",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>不听从王命，王、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王太后</span>势弱孤立不能制服，使者怯懦无决断。又认为王、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王太后</span>已归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>作乱，不足以兴大兵，想派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄参</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千人</span>前去出使。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄参\">参（庄参）</span>说：\"以友好方式前去，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数人</span>就够了；以武力前去，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千人</span>不足以有所作为。\" 推辞不去，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>就罢免了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄参\">参（庄参）</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郏</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span>、前任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">济北相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩千秋</span>奋然说：\"凭区区南越，又有王、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>为内应，只有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>为害，愿得到勇<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百人</span>，必能<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>首级以报。\" 于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派遣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩千秋\">千秋（韩千秋）</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王太后</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樛乐</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千人</span>前往，进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>境内。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>等人于是反叛，下令国中说：\"王年幼。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>人，又与使者淫乱，一心想内属汉朝，把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝器</span>全部带去进献<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>以讨好汉廷，带很多人随行，到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，把他们当俘虏卖作奴仆。只<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>一时脱身之利，不顾<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>，无<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">万世（时长）</span>长远之谋。\" 就与其弟率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了王、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>及<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝使者。派人告谕<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苍梧</span>的秦王及各郡县，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵婴齐\">明王（赵婴齐）</span>的长子、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>籍妻子所生之子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">术阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵建德\">建德（赵建德）</span>为王。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩千秋</span>的军队进入南越，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>了几个小邑。后来<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人故意让道供给粮食，汉军行至距<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十里</span>时，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人用兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩千秋\">千秋（韩千秋）</span>等，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了汉军。派人用匣子封装<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝使者的符节置于边塞上，说些漂亮的谎言谢罪，又发兵守住要害之处。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩千秋</span>虽然没有成功，也是全军的先锋之冠。\" 封他的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩延年\">延年（韩延年）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">成安侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樛乐</span>，其姐为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王太后</span>，首倡归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝，封他的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樛广德\">广德（樛广德）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">龙亢侯</span>。于是下<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span>令说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>衰微，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>以武力征伐，当时人讥讽做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的不去讨贼。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵建德\">建德（赵建德）</span>等人反叛，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为王安然自若，命令罪人及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>以南的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">楼船</span>十万大军前去讨伐。\""
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "汉军平定南越",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎五年秋</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">路博德</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波将军</span>，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桂阳</span>出发，顺<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汇水</span>而下；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">主爵都尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨仆</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span>出发，顺<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">横浦</span>而下；原先的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">归义越侯</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">戈船</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">下厉将军</span>，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">零陵</span>出发，一支顺<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">离水</span>而下，一支抵达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苍梧</span>；派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">驰义侯</span>率领<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>的罪人，征发<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夜郎</span>的军队，顺<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牂柯江</span>而下：都会合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "空",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎六年冬</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>率领精兵先<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻陷</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寻陕</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">石门</span>，获得越人的船只和粮食，乘势推进，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">挫</span>败越人的锋芒，率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>等候<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>军。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波将军</span>率领罪人，路途遥远，比约期晚到，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>会合时只有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀人</span>，于是一同进军。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>军在前，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵建德\">建德（赵建德）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>都据城而守。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>自己选择有利之处，占据东南面；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>占据西北面。到傍晚时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人，放火烧城。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人一向听闻<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>的名声，天色已晚，不知他兵力多少。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>于是扎营，派使者招降，赐给印信，又放降者回去互相招降。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>奋力<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击焚烧敌军，反而把敌军驱赶进入<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>营中。天将破晓，城中都向<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>投降。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵建德\">建德（赵建德）</span>已在夜里与其部属<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百人</span>逃入海中，乘船向西而去。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>又询问所俘获的降者中的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span>，得知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>的去向，派人追击。以原来的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏弘</span>俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵建德\">建德（赵建德）</span>，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">海常侯</span>；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越郎</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">都稽</span>俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕嘉\">嘉（吕嘉）</span>，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">临蔡侯</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "空",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苍梧</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵光</span>，是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>王的同姓，听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵到来，以及<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>地<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">揭阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：史定\">定（史定）</span>自行归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝；<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>地<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桂林</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">监</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">居翁</span>谕告<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">瓯骆</span>归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝：都得以封侯。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">戈船</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">下厉将军</span>的军队和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">驰义侯</span>所征发的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夜郎</span>军队还未到达，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>已经平定。于是设为九郡。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波将军</span>增加封邑。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>的军队因为攻陷坚城而被封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将梁侯</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "空",
      "text": "从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">尉佗（赵佗）</span>开始称王以后，传<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五世</span>历<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九十三岁（时长）</span>而国亡。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "太史公论赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说： <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">尉佗（赵佗）</span>之所以称王，本来源于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任嚣</span>的谋划。 遭逢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝初定天下，得以列入<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：隆虑侯灶\">隆虑（隆虑侯灶）</span>的军队遭遇湿热瘟疫，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>得以愈发骄横。 <span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">瓯骆</span>相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>伐，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>动荡摇摆。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵临境，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>入朝。 其后亡国，征兆出自<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">樛</span>氏之女； <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>小忠守主，却使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>无后嗣。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>随心所欲，怠慢骄傲而致迷惑； <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伏波</span>身处困境，智谋愈发增长，转祸为福。 成<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>之间的转换，就像纠缠的绳索。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中原</span>群鹿奔逃，群雄无法制服。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝军事向西驱驰，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>人权势在南方边陲。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>施展辩才，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">尉他（赵佗）</span>去掉帝号。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樛太后\">嫪后（樛太后）</span>在内朝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕嘉</span>凶狠狼戾。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君臣</span>不和协，最终遭到剿灭抛弃。"
    }
  }
}